e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/157231/', '', 'Tocainide, Dronedarone, Dofetilide, Bretylium, Moricizine, Ibutilide', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, Belumosudil, More', 1767369485);
